- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is relevant as the paper deals with extracting relevant concepts from unstructured clinical texts. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is a possibility as the paper discusses issues related to data quality and annotation in a clinical context. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with issues related to the accuracy and reliability of information extraction systems.
